{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a PuyoPuyo fan or simply a lover of arcade puzzles? Dive into the colorful world of Mayo Mayo, inspired by fast food, sauces and condiments. Play with Blue, Mustard, Mayo, Wasabi, and Ketchup in this Match-4 puzzle that will challenge your reflexes and wits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Demo offers a glimpse of the different modes: the first world of Puzzle mode with 20 levels, 5 minutes of Survival mode on easy difficulty, and multiplayer matches against easy AI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/PuzzleMode.gif?t=1731057027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With the Puzzle mode, pull off spectacular combos. Sharpen your thinking and reaction skills through 160 progressively challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/MultiMode.gif?t=1731057027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump into Multiplayer mode, locally or online, with friends or players from around the world. Create public or private games with up to 4 players. Plus, you can challenge AI opponents of all skill levels to improve, but be warned\u2014they won\u2019t go easy on you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/SurvivalMode.gif?t=1731057027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Love breaking records? The Survival mode, with its 3 difficulty levels, offers an endless experience to push your limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/TrainingMode.gif?t=1731057027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Training mode lets you tweak various settings to hone your skills. Take your time to master this game\u2014easy to pick up, but hard to master!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731057027","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/page.bg.jpg?t=1731057027","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/5c66014dc92b131197786d3ed064a86e1bfea896/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731057027","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/5c66014dc92b131197786d3ed064a86e1bfea896/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731057027","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you a PuyoPuyo fan or simply a lover of arcade puzzles? Dive into the colorful world of Mayo Mayo, inspired by fast food, sauces and condiments. Play with Blue, Mustard, Mayo, Wasabi, and Ketchup in this Match-4 puzzle that will challenge your reflexes and wits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Demo offers a glimpse of the different modes: the first world of Puzzle mode with 20 levels, 5 minutes of Survival mode on easy difficulty, and multiplayer matches against easy AI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/PuzzleMode.gif?t=1731057027\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With the Puzzle mode, pull off spectacular combos. Sharpen your thinking and reaction skills through 160 progressively challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.